				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The workers are discussing a third worker who skipped on the job. That’s the third one they lose. At this pace they’re never going to fix up the wall! If talked to you learned the missing person stayed working late in the evening - they probably went to drink afterwards and passed out."
